skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: kitty trivia
des:
A simple trivia game to test your knowledge about Hello Kitty. Start the game by saying "Alexa Start Kitty Trivia". The trivia will give you multiple choice answers. Reply with the number of the correct answer. E.g.

Alexa: "What is the color of Hello Kitty's hair bow? 1 : Red, 2: Pink, 3: Blue, 4: Yellow"
User: "1"
Alexa: "Correct. Your score is 2"

Note: This skill is not sponsored or endorsed by Hello Kitty. It is an unofficial (fan) version.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
